or 30 years ago.

8
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:24,200
So is it just because of the amount of online time that children have now, which obviously

9
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,880
happens indoors?

10
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:32,520
Well, if that was the case, there'd be a correlation between high internet use and low levels

11
