large or small groups.

45
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:50,080
But the fact that the play sessions don't go on for as long.

46
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:55,640
And games involving one child running after another who tries to get away, these are

47
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:58,360
still as popular as ever.

48
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:02,000
But one thing that is declined is improvised games.

49
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:05,040
And I'd like to examine why this might be.

50
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,920
Interesting.

51
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:08,920
And what about safety?

52
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:13,760
Well, from my reading, serious accidents are still rare.

53
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:21,360
More kids hurt themselves falling out of bed than out of trees.

54
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:26,560
